 A video of an armed robbery that happened in Blairgowrie in Randburg on Saturday, is doing the rounds on social media. In the CCTV footage shared by a group called, Stolen Cars RSA, a white Mercedes Benz Vito can be seen pulling into a driveway, as a woman and a child walk along the street. As the Vito enters the yard and woman and child get past the gate, a white Mercedes Benz C-Class comes at high speed nearly knocking the child over. The thugs then get out of the car and rush into the yard, in an effort to get away from the thugs, the driver of the Vito can then be seen reversing into the property's wall and hitting it. WATCH VIDEO BELOW: 